review 1: Stunning waterfall, have 2 waterfall the highest is 120 meters but we just can see from above no access to go down, but we stil can enjoy the  35 meters, and also have swimming pool with green view
review 2: Place where there are 2 hidden waterfalls. The smaller waterfall can be reached in 20mins walking down on steps, the larger waterfall can be seen from the top, but unfortunately we did not find the way down. According to some local people there is no path but we heard from others that from down on other part of the valley can be reached.
review 3:
This place still natural, the long way down to the waterfall will challenge you...
So if you want to come, just be ready for the adventure!
